{"tid":1785282,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"1224晩, 1225和1226約定你, 和你Shop, 一星期時間宣傳定差不多","createTime":"2019-12-16T09:13:50.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-16T09:16:13.000Z","uid":76310,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"89f80f548b2bb60f87912e0ca6ff2361c65c2ca7","tid":1785282,"uid":76310,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-16T09:13:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ezU4fNh.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FezU4fNh.jpg&h=28a74d10&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n手足整既文宣<br />\n不過我覺得有幾個地方要修正(我的建議已經考慮埋分區地點, 交通, 距離和散水問題)<br />\n1. 中環IFC要取消, 因為銅鑼灣分左中環既人, 2個地點太近, 而且放假, 中環附近無街坊(刪去中環IFC)<br />\n2. 觀塘APM同九龍灣德福太近, 會分左人流, 因為德福太仆街, 所以留德福(刪去觀塘APM)<br />\n3. 加上水廣場, 方便北區人仕(加上水廣場)<br />\n4. 加荃新天地, 方便荃灣葵青青衣人仕(加荃新天地)<br />\n<br />\n1224<br />\n時間: 1900-2200<br />\n<br />\n1225<br />\n時間:1400-2200<br />\n<br />\n1226<br />\n時間:1400-2200<br />\n<br />\n而家宣傳定差不多<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d8dbf1ea540daec79e6426e66a2d90f3e11c2765","tid":1785282,"uid":34816,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-16T09:15:53.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"698cd855b8bd789cf2e7c83caf15351a5aca3292","tid":1785282,"uid":76310,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-16T09:16:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}